{"tid":2409862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"管浩鳴：陳同佳仍住在警方安排的安全屋　冀台灣當局盡快發簽證","createTime":"2021-02-16T07:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T08:42:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c8195826ecc96d9a5b4e37a25e74f2f445462de7","tid":2409862,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"台灣殺人案疑犯陳同佳至今仍未到台灣自首。<br />\n<br />\n聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴回應傳媒查詢時表示，台灣當局並未向陳同佳發出簽證，台灣的代表律師已多次聯絡有關「窗口」，表達陳同佳願意回台自首，但至今未有正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴希望台灣當局本着人道考慮，盡快發出簽證。他又指出，陳同佳仍身處香港，住在警方安排的「安全屋」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575870-20210216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575870-20210216.htm&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=13d71291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575870-20210216.htm&h=f86b6681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575870-20210216.htm</a>"},{"pid":"eedc37c0b3eac96bf877a98592813424f489ea92","tid":2409862,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"支那肺炎下最大贏家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ec1ad14b4742330b2423bb32b12db3048f2009","tid":2409862,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c92c51c73552a292f7e1b463bf16f256056ec16","tid":2409862,"uid":63543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"台灣：個殺人犯係你道，你咪唔好撚俾佢過來囉，搞到好似我求你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /